name: Jumbo Afterstory (Demo)
description:
Do you think Monika Afterstory is too WELL MADE, and has a severe lack of furries? No fear, for I have created Jumbo Afterstory! A WIP passion project where you be friends with a goofy lil furry named Jumby! Please note this is a SEVERELY unfinished project, the buttons don't work yet.

Click and stuff and be friends!!!
